{
  "chapter": 7,
  "chapter_summary": "第七回\"骨血\"讲述老人将幼年李坏带回家中的往事。老人告诉李坏他是李家的骨血，只要保持骨气便不会被人轻贱。李坏自认从头坏到脚，老人却坚信他本质不坏。九年后李坏再次回家，物是人非，他已练成天下无双的绝技，找到了富可敌国的宝藏。本章通过回忆与现实的对比，揭示李坏的身世背景和李家以骨气传家的家风。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "你要带我到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "带你回家去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "回家？我哪里有家？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你有的。我相信你一定会以你的家为荣，你的家也一定会以你为荣。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "以我为荣？像我这么样一个已经从头顶坏到脚底坏透子的坏小孩？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你不坏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "我还不坏？怎么样才算坏？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "能做得出那种卑鄙无耻下流的事的人才算坏。可是你做不出。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "你怎么知道我做不出？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "因为你是李家的人，是李家的骨血。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "只要你能保持这一点骨气，我也敢保证世界上绝没有任何人敢对你有一点轻贱。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    }
  ],
